How to begin installation:

1) Change script1 and script2 file permission typing:
    chmod u=+rwx script1 script2

2) Run script1 typing:
    ./script1

3) Update .bashrc typing:
    source $HOME/.bashrc

4) Run script2 typing:
    ./script2

WARNNING: These scripts drives an OPTIMIZED installation of all packages. If you are looking for a DEBUGGING installation, be my guest to change the settings.

